    This is the internal type for Timestamp with time zone. The full qualified input format of Timestamp with time zone is "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss[.SSS...] zoneid/zoneoffset", where the time and zone parts are optional. If time part is absent, a default '00:00:00.0' will be used. If zone part is absent, the system time zone will be used.
